A collaboration with Scornhex exploring the concept of “body and soul”. This collaboration
was a process of exploring and combining our creative ideas and artistic styles into two
artworks that form a whole. Both Scornhex and I contributed to both pieces of the collab. I’m
a massive fan of Scornhex’s work so I encourage you to check out his part of the collab on
his HEN account and his other works.
